features.description: Initialize Flutter project with proper structure, pubspec.yaml dependencies (provider, hive, home_widget, uuid, intl, google_fonts, flutter_animate), and basic configuration
Implement feature-based folder structure: lib/core/, lib/features/affirmations/, lib/features/settings/, lib/features/onboarding/, lib/widgets/native_widget/
Configure Hive for local storage with proper initialization, type adapters for Affirmation model, and platform-specific paths
Set up Provider/Riverpod for state management with AffirmationProvider and SettingsProvider
Create Affirmation class with id (UUID), text (max 280 chars), createdAt, updatedAt, displayCount, isActive fields. Include Hive type adapter
Implement functionality to create new affirmations with free-form text input, character limit validation (280 chars), and UUID generation
Implement functionality to edit existing affirmations, updating the updatedAt timestamp and preserving other metadata
Implement functionality to delete affirmations with confirmation dialog
Implement functionality to view all saved affirmations in a scrollable list with proper empty state handling
Support multi-line text input and display for affirmations
Implement drag-and-drop reordering of affirmations in the list view
Create AffirmationRepository for CRUD operations with Hive, abstracting storage implementation
Implement GetRandomAffirmation use case that selects a random active affirmation, avoiding immediate repetition
Implement settings storage for theme, refreshMode, and language preferences using Hive
Implement export functionality to save affirmations to a text file
Implement import functionality to load affirmations from a text file
Configure AppTheme with zen color palette (Cloud White, Deep Night, Soft Sage, etc.), typography (Playfair Display, Inter), and consistent styling
Implement theme switching between light, dark, and system modes with proper color adaptation
Create main home screen displaying a random affirmation with zen animation, navigation to affirmation list, and settings
Implement subtle fade-in animation (300-500ms) for affirmation transitions and optional breathing animation
Enable swipe or tap gesture on home screen to display another random affirmation with smooth transition
Add refresh button on home screen to cycle through affirmations
Create screen displaying all affirmations in a card-based list with edit/delete actions
Create screen for creating/editing affirmations with text input, character counter, and save/cancel actions
Create reusable AffirmationCard widget with zen styling, rounded corners (16px), soft elevation, and proper text display
Create reusable AffirmationInput widget with multi-line support, character limit indicator, and validation
Create settings screen with theme toggle, refresh interval options, language selection, and font size adjustment
Design and implement empty state for affirmation list with illustration and 'Create Your First Affirmation' prompt
Create welcome screen with illustration and brief app explanation for first-time users
Implement complete first-launch onboarding: welcome -> create first affirmation -> success animation -> widget setup instructions
Implement confirmation dialog for affirmation deletion with cancel/confirm actions
Implement font size adjustment setting for accessibility with preview
Integrate home_widget package and configure platform channels for iOS and Android widget communication
Implement data sharing between Flutter app and native widgets using SharedDefaults (iOS) and SharedPreferences (Android)
Create iOS WidgetKit extension with SwiftUI for small (2x2), medium (4x2), and large (4x4) widget sizes
Implement TimelineProvider for iOS widget with refresh on device unlock events
Create Android AppWidgetProvider with Kotlin for small, medium, and large widget sizes
Implement BroadcastReceiver for ACTION_USER_PRESENT to update widget on phone unlock
Configure widget tap action to launch main application
Display placeholder text when no affirmations exist in the widget
Trigger widget refresh when affirmations are added, modified, or deleted in the app
Adapt widget appearance to system light/dark mode with translucent background and blur effect
Implement setting to enable/disable widget affirmation rotation
Implement setting for refresh interval: every unlock, hourly, or daily
Optimize app initialization to achieve cold start time under 2 seconds
Ensure widget updates complete within 500ms of trigger event
Optimize memory usage to stay under 50MB footprint
Ensure 100% of features work offline without internet connection
Verify no analytics, tracking, or data collection is implemented in v1
Ensure core functionality works without internet permission
Implement platform-native encryption for local data storage
Verify no third-party SDKs that collect user data are included
Implement full VoiceOver support for iOS with proper semantic labels
Implement full TalkBack support for Android with proper content descriptions
Ensure all interactive elements have minimum 44x44 points touch target
Verify all text meets minimum 4.5:1 color contrast ratio
Support system font scaling for users with visual impairments
Configure Flutter localization with intl package, ARB files for French and English
